Best Buy details a season pass for <em><a href="http://www.joystiq.com/game/assassins-creed-4-black-flag">Assassin's Creed 4: Black Flag</a> </em>highlighting pirate protagonist Edward Kenway's first mate, Adewale, as a playable character. The <a href="http://www.bestbuy.com/site/Assassin%27s+Creed+IV+Black+Flag+Season+Pass+-+PS3+%5BDigital+Download+Add-On%5D/1000003800.p?id=1000003799&amp;skuId=1000003800&amp;st=1000003800&amp;lp=1&amp;cp=1#tab=overviewwww.bestbuy.com/site/Assassin%27s+Creed+IV+Black+Flag+Season+Pass+">Best Buy listing</a> says this content will take players "even deeper into the real explosive events of the Golden Age of Pirates."<br />
<br />
<em>Assassin's Creed 4: Black Flag</em>'s season pass will cost $20, Best Buy says, and will include both single-player and multiplayer content. The cost for these packs piecemeal is $40 according to the listing.<br />
<br />
Season passes are hardly new to the Assassin's Creed franchise. In <em>Assassin's Creed 3</em>, season pass content revolved around an alternate story focusing on <a href="http://www.joystiq.com/tag/the-tyranny-of-king-washington/">a tyrannical King George Washington</a>. Ubisoft has previously stated PlayStation platforms will have <a href="http://www.joystiq.com/2013/06/12/assassins-creed-4-exclusive-playstation-content-continues-aveli/">exclusive <em>Assassin's Creed 4</em> content</a> highlighting the story of the <em>Assassin's Creed 3: Liberation</em> heroine, Aveline.<p style="padding:5px;background:#ffffcc;border:1px solid #ffff99;clear:both;"><a href="http://www.joystiq.com"><img src="http://www.blogsmithmedia.com/www.joystiq.com/media/feedlogo.gif" alt="Joystiq" style="float:left;padding:0 5px 5px 0;" /></a><a href="http://www.joystiq.com/2013/06/21/assassins-creed-4-listing-points-to-first-mate-dlc-in-season-pa/">Assassin's Creed 4 listing points to first mate DLC in season pass</a> originally appeared on <a href="http://www.joystiq.com">Joystiq</a> on Fri, 21 Jun 2013 08:00:00 EST.  Please see our <a href="http://www.weblogsinc.com/feed-terms/">terms for use of feeds</a>.<br style="clear:both;"></p><h6 style="clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;"></h6><a href="http://www.joystiq.com/2013/06/21/assassins-creed-4-listing-points-to-first-mate-dlc-in-season-pa/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent link to this entry">Permalink</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="http://www.joystiq.com/forward/20630559/" title="Send this entry to a friend via email">Email this</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="http://www.joystiq.com/2013/06/21/assassins-creed-4-listing-points-to-first-mate-dlc-in-season-pa/#comments" title="View reader comments on this entry">Comments</a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:13:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"adewale";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s