Sean Gibbons, Community Coordinator at Wizards of the Coast, walks us through one of the big additions in <em><a href="http://www.joystiq.com/game/magic-2014-duels-of-the-planeswalkers">Magic 2014: Duels of the Planeswalkers</a></em>: the Sealed Campaign. Essentially, players open a set number of sealed booster packs and build a deck from those cards, limiting the pool of available cards and adding an element of randomness to duels - a popular play type in the physical format.<br />
<br />
