<a href="http://www.joystiq.com/game/mario-kart-8"><em>Mario Kart 8</em></a> takes the series in a new direction, which is to say, "sideways." The Wii U's first entry in the franchise introduces the concept of relativistic gravity - an idea <a href="http://www.joystiq.com/game/super-mario-galaxy">not entirely foreign</a> to Mario himself - to the vehicular antics enjoyed by Nintendo's mascots.<br />
<br />
